{"tid":1981902,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港2月至今　汽油價僅減6%","createTime":"2020-04-21T02:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T03:04:08.000Z","uid":160964,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"274891041427bf47c446a10b8a799841f77c8884","tid":1981902,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:35:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200421/AXEZEVI34L676SAXTFPVY4X4UY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200421%2FAXEZEVI34L676SAXTFPVY4X4UY%2F&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=029f5381\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200421%2FAXEZEVI34L676SAXTFPVY4X4UY%2F&h=1733e322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200421/AXEZEVI34L676SAXTFPVY4X4UY/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】紐約期油和布蘭特期油分別自今年初高位每桶63.27美元和68.71美元，累跌逾六至七成，現時每公升油價折算約0.72港元，較蒸餾水每公升5.08港元更低。然而，香港油公司的燃油零售價格，減幅卻未有跟隨。<br />\n<br />\n本港各油公司價格相若，以蜆殼（Shell）為例，2月初普通汽油價格為每公升17.74元，昨日每公升16.64元，減幅為6.2%。蜆殼表示，本港車用燃油以入口為主，故公司會以新加坡燃油離岸價作為成本計算之一。坊間經常提到的原油價格，並不適用於本港燃油市場。<br />\n加德士：會提供折扣<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：興隆隱瞞62億虧損 滙控遭殃<br />\n<br />\n雪佛龍回應指，油價調整除了考慮成品油的入口價格，也要衡量市場狀況及公司的各種經營成本如地價、地租、差餉、運輸等，旗下加德士亦會提供各種折扣優惠回饋顧客。埃克森美孚（Esso）則稱，經常檢討燃油零售價，自1月底以來，已9次下調車用燃油產品零售價。<br />\n<br />\n香港燃油價格一向高冠全球，<a href=\"http://根據國際油價監察網站globalpetrolprices.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99globalpetrolprices.com&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=42099ec1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">根據國際油價監察網站globalpetrolprices.com</a> 4月份數據顯示，香港車用汽油平均每公升16.74元，位居榜首，比排名第二的中非共和國每公升14.2元貴近兩成。"},{"pid":"e5446b27aa2696ee27b1bf7fb4b809a21d8a093e","tid":1981902,"uid":72058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed41233a7dfca16f80ee44eeb9f9f894c8b3bd8","tid":1981902,"uid":92118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"屌你班油公司，加就毫幾咁上，減就幾仙？<br />\nESSO仲好笑，減9次價又點？<br />\n由18蚊減到16.64，減9次加埋都只係減唔到2蚊你都好意思講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5702eb8908085683c50fb275888b3807db2ad1","tid":1981902,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"成本就轉嫁，利潤就攞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc8178767f785f3b7fdaeb7c869f2113e5b0f38","tid":1981902,"uid":26976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"有冇得call香港油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係無得輸"},{"pid":"bfc9ca1e1e9b5e47e23644cf9460da033b09cab8","tid":1981902,"uid":92118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"香港學下人地澳門喇，8蚊一升汽油呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"d3d69d448ad928df1e4576ad74398c788842c945","tid":1981902,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5446b27aa2696ee27b1bf7fb4b809a21d8a093e","tid":1981902,"uid":72058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"反競爭委員會一早有report 屌過哩個市場<br />\n不過冇証據"},{"pid":"7795f7a6bc0dade309f54e6ed5b676deec3b7156","tid":1981902,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"人哋話提煉，運輸等成本上漲 只能。夠減少少"},{"pid":"6f261f21d0fec5d2810b35f48657dde4157da79a","tid":1981902,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT